title: Moustache Mountain 040116
description: It is said, that an ancient civilization once made a Moustache Gel so good, that noone could resist you after you had applied it. All was good for them, the girls loved them, the men admired, and they were on track to conquer the whole world, however a terrible sickness once struck them, and wiped out all, but one man.. With his last breath, the last living man of the ancient civilization, managed to climb the highest flying mountain and hide the last remaining Moustache Gel there
